headline: Lam Research Resets Around Micron Partnership And Specialty Chip Expansion
summary: Lam Research (NasdaqGS:LRCX) has opened a new office in Boise to deepen collaboration with key customer Micron Technology on semiconductor development. The company also announced a new partnership with CEA-Leti focused on next generation specialty semiconductor technology devices. Leadership changes were introduced alongside these moves, signaling an internal reset of responsibilities and focus areas.
